<div type="edition" xml:lang="tel-Latn" rendition="class:telugu maturity:vernacular">

<p>
<lb n="1"/>svasti śrī <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> śākābdē saptarāmatriśaśiparimitē māsi vaiśākhasaṁjñē vakṣē śuklē tṛtī
<lb n="2" break="no"/>yēhani naraharayē kāvyavārē pradīpaṁ <supplied reason="undefined"><g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g></supplied> prādādācaṁdratāraṁ harigirivatayēkhaṁḍami
<lb n="3" break="no"/>ṣṭārtthasiddhyai śrīman śrīvatsagōtrōdbhavavaraharirājāryyanāmā guṇāḍhyaḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> śākavaru
<lb n="4" break="no"/>ṣaṁbulu 1337 gunēṁṭi vaiśākha śukla tṛtīyā śukravāramunāṁḍu rāya
<lb n="5" break="no"/>purāna ḍāhāḷa mahēśvaranāyani koḍuku harirājanāyaṁḍu tanakunu Iṣṭā
<lb n="6" break="no"/>rththasiddhigānu sihyādrināthani sammukhamaṁdunu nityamunu veluṁguṭakunu Akhaṁ
<lb n="7" break="no"/>ḍadīpamu pratimasaItamugānu peṭṭenu Iṁdula samarunakai khillāri
<lb n="8" break="no"/>purādhisēnāpati koḍuku bairi Ītani tammuṁḍu gaṁgana Iddaṟavaśānannu peṭṭina
<lb n="9"/>mōdālu 50 Ītani kūḍujītānakunu<note n="439-1">Blank space fornu in the original.</note>puṭyaṁḍu kṣētramu
<lb n="10"/>konipeṭṭenu Ī kṣētramu bhujiṁci Itaṁḍu bhaṁḍāranaku nelakunu Ēḍu <unclear>dū</unclear>
<lb n="11" break="no"/>muṁga kuṁcaṁḍu neyi peṭṭaṁgalāṁḍu Ā(ṁ)caṁdrārkkastayigānu I dharmu śrīvai
<lb n="12" break="no"/>ṣṇava rakṣa <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> śatruṇāpi kṛtō dharmmaḥ pālanīyō manīṣibhiḥ <g ref="sym:bar" type="punctuation">.</g> śatrurēva hi śatru
<lb n="13" break="no"/>syadarmma<supplied reason="omitted">ḥ</supplied> śatrurnna kasyacit <g ref="sym:doubleBar" type="punctuation">.</g> śrī śrī śrī
</p>

